  "subject": "Split PyPI templates for CBS docker client",
  "commit_message": "Split PyPI templates for CBS docker client\n\nThis module is in a subdirectory, so must specify a gerrit trigger\nfile path to test this module and package it into a distribution for\nupload to PyPI.  But that parameter breaks the release verify and\nmerge jobs. Work around the problem by using two project defs.\nAlso configure the non-release merge job with repo key pypy-test.\n\nSigned-off-by: Lott, Christopher (cl778h) <cl778h@att.com>\nIssue-ID: DCAEGEN2-1729\nChange-Id: I5ab67a95d7e3f40cd2241ef69ea22bf0f9ce9b7f\n",
